metadata.name: #6 No-Hopeful
metadata.description:
I don't see a way forward. Do these monsters want me to be unhappy? There will be happier worlds under that bright moon, will you help me enter that world? It seems like a world that is not at all happy, but under the moon shining in the distance, there must be a world full of great happiness.

300DPI, 7000 X 6000 px

By Bluemingg
